text: Aase Othlo Barfod Clausen (1914 - 2005) was a Danish model and movie actress. She was the fifth Miss Europe. She was the first Danish to get the title. She also won the fifth title of the Miss Denmark beauty contest. She also participated in the 1932 edition of Miss Universe. == References == == Other websites == * Category:1914 births Category:2005 deaths Category:Danish movie actors Category:Beauty pageant winners
